Class MapSetter

java.lang.Object
  org.kohsuke.args4j.MapSetter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Setter
public class MapSetter
extends Object
implements Setter

This setter adds a new entry to a Map. The value which is passed is split into the Map-key and Map-value by a "=".

-map key=value
